title: Cafe Natasha's Kabob International
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Take-out, Catering, Middle Eastern, Persian, Iranian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Persian cuisine restaurant. Offers a separate vegetarian menu with choices for appetizers, main entrees and pita wraps; vegan items are labeled. Sample dishes such as veggie koubideh combo platter, rice and curry veggie platter, stuffed pepper and tomato, vegan falafel platter, shami platter (veggie patties). Has gluten-free.
